      <title>Euronext看到钱在支出中搬到欧洲，美国重新考虑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/euronext-sees-money-moving-to-europe-amid-spending-us-rethink</link>
      <description><![CDATA[EuroNext NV首席执行官Stephane Boujnah表示，由于政府支出的前景和投资者重新评估了美国市场，投资者正在越来越多地将资金转移到欧洲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/euronext-sees-money-moving-to-europe-amid-spending-us-rethink</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 07:56:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
